description: Contact profile is a reusable contact configuration.

commands.name: az orbital contact-profile create
commands.syntax:
az orbital contact-profile create --contact-profile-name
                                  --resource-group
                                  [--auto-tracking {disabled, sBand, xBand}]
                                  [--event-hub-uri]
                                  [--links]
                                  [--location]
                                  [--min-elevation]
                                  [--min-viable-duration]
                                  [--network-configuration]
                                  [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                  [--tags]

commands.name: az orbital contact-profile delete
commands.summary: Delete a specified contact profile resource.
commands.syntax:
az orbital contact-profile delete [--contact-profile-name]
                                  [--ids]
                                  [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                  [--resource-group]
                                  [--subscription]
                                  [--yes]

commands.name: az orbital contact-profile show
commands.summary: Get the specified contact Profile in a specified resource group.

commands.name: az orbital contact-profile update
commands.syntax:
az orbital contact-profile update [--add]
                                  [--auto-tracking {disabled, sBand, xBand}]
                                  [--contact-profile-name]
                                  [--event-hub-uri]
                                  [--force-string {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                  [--ids]
                                  [--links]
                                  [--location]
                                  [--min-elevation]
                                  [--min-viable-duration]
                                  [--network-configuration]
                                  [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                  [--remove]
                                  [--resource-group]
                                  [--set]
                                  [--subscription]
                                  [--tags]

commands.name: az orbital contact-profile wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition is met.
